WEBVTT

01:02.680 --> 01:03.410
You're here.

01:03.800 --> 01:04.440
Have a seat.

01:04.440 --> 01:05.160
Sorry.

01:05.360 --> 01:06.680
Have you been waiting long?

01:06.680 --> 01:07.440
No.

01:07.520 --> 01:08.360
I just got here too.

01:08.360 --> 01:09.420
Let's order first.

01:09.440 --> 01:10.600
Let me say this first,

01:10.600 --> 01:11.400
it's my treat.

01:11.840 --> 01:12.600
To thank you

01:12.600 --> 01:14.730
for taking me to your school's museum.

01:15.200 --> 01:16.930
Then I'll order the whole menu.

01:17.080 --> 01:19.280
You can order the whole menu if you want.

01:19.640 --> 01:21.080
Waiter, we'd like to order.

01:21.080 --> 01:21.680
Coming.

01:24.200 --> 01:25.260
Here's your water.

01:25.320 --> 01:25.840
Pizza.

01:27.520 --> 01:28.480
And a tiramisu.

01:29.000 --> 01:29.320
Okay.

01:29.320 --> 01:30.160
Some popcorn chicken.

01:30.160 --> 01:30.600
Okay.

01:30.880 --> 01:31.480
That's it.

01:32.039 --> 01:33.570
Okay, please wait a moment.

01:34.880 --> 01:37.210
Didn't you say you'd order the whole menu?

01:37.560 --> 01:39.560
I want to save the rest for next time.

01:41.200 --> 01:43.039
Look how pretty you are when you smile.

01:43.039 --> 01:44.300
You should smile more.

01:45.039 --> 01:47.840
Last time I saw you at the Jingdezhen Imperial Kiln Museum,

01:47.840 --> 01:50.880
you were sitting there alone, looking very disappointed.

01:50.880 --> 01:51.640
What's wrong?

01:51.640 --> 01:53.100
Is something on your mind?

01:54.720 --> 01:56.320
Are you sure you want to hear it?

01:56.320 --> 01:57.650
It will take a long time.

02:03.680 --> 02:04.800
So,

02:05.040 --> 02:07.200
you have a friend who's helping to

02:07.200 --> 02:08.919
set you up with another guy.

02:09.199 --> 02:10.759
But a girl

02:10.759 --> 02:11.880
got in your friend's way.

02:11.880 --> 02:12.400
Right.

02:12.520 --> 02:13.840
Then your friend

02:13.840 --> 02:15.160
went and blamed this girl.

02:15.160 --> 02:15.640
Right.

02:15.640 --> 02:17.400
And you spoke up for this girl.

02:17.800 --> 02:18.520
So,

02:19.320 --> 02:21.650
your friend turned around and blamed you.

02:23.480 --> 02:25.079
I have to say, this whole thing...

02:25.079 --> 02:26.320
Trust me.

02:26.920 --> 02:28.600
If you were in my shoes,

02:29.320 --> 02:30.780
you'd be just as troubled.

02:30.960 --> 02:32.440
Believe me.

02:32.880 --> 02:35.280
I wouldn't run into a situation like yours.

02:35.960 --> 02:36.560
True.

02:37.320 --> 02:39.040
Sometimes I really envy you.

02:39.280 --> 02:40.560
It seems like you can handle anything

02:40.560 --> 02:41.920
with ease.

02:44.480 --> 02:45.600
Not really.

02:46.160 --> 02:47.620
I have my own troubles too.

02:48.280 --> 02:50.040
And recently, because of this,

02:50.320 --> 02:52.050
I've been too anxious to sleep.

02:52.680 --> 02:53.480
What's wrong?

02:54.360 --> 02:57.120
My job at the Jingdezhen Imperial Kiln Museum is temporary.

02:57.120 --> 02:59.840
So I've always wanted to become a full-time employee.

02:59.840 --> 03:01.000
But the last two times,

03:01.000 --> 03:02.800
I failed at the final interview.

03:02.840 --> 03:05.440
I qualified for the interview again this time.

03:06.040 --> 03:08.570
But thinking about failing the last two times

03:08.720 --> 03:10.120
makes me really nervous.

03:10.600 --> 03:12.520
I get so anxious that I can't sleep.

03:12.520 --> 03:13.380
I didn't expect

03:13.640 --> 03:15.170
you to have this side to you.

03:15.720 --> 03:16.920
So I should thank you.

03:17.680 --> 03:18.810
Every time I see you,

03:19.079 --> 03:20.480
I feel much more relaxed.

03:24.640 --> 03:25.880
This is how this move is done, right?

03:25.880 --> 03:26.680
Like this.

03:26.720 --> 03:27.400
Students,

03:27.880 --> 03:29.079
starting from today,

03:29.600 --> 03:31.000
we will begin

03:31.280 --> 03:34.520
the study and research of the kintsugi restoration process.

03:34.520 --> 03:36.360
The first step of the kintsugi process

03:36.360 --> 03:38.320
is to use raw lacquer to solidify the base.

03:38.320 --> 03:39.840
This involves applying the raw lacquer

03:39.840 --> 03:42.170
onto the broken sections of the ceramics,

03:42.400 --> 03:43.730
joining them together,

03:43.920 --> 03:46.680
and then drying them in a kiln.

03:47.079 --> 03:48.079
This raw lacquer,

03:48.200 --> 03:49.400
as the name suggests,

03:49.440 --> 03:52.360
is a substance formed

03:52.640 --> 03:55.240
after the sap of the lacquer tree is collected.

03:56.560 --> 03:58.280
After this substance dries,

03:58.600 --> 03:59.680
it's resistant to corrosion

03:59.680 --> 04:00.400
and heat,

04:00.680 --> 04:03.520
and also has a beautiful color and luster.

04:04.520 --> 04:06.440
When applied to ceramics,

04:06.640 --> 04:08.040
it's not only practical,

04:08.280 --> 04:09.760
but also adds

04:09.960 --> 04:12.560
color and gloss to the objects.

04:55.480 --> 04:56.280
Class is over.

04:57.159 --> 04:57.960
Class is over.

04:58.120 --> 04:59.200
Want to eat together?

04:59.200 --> 05:00.360
I have something to do.

05:00.360 --> 05:01.280
I'll go first. Bye.

05:01.280 --> 05:01.920
Bye.

05:03.640 --> 05:04.700
What are you doing?

05:05.000 --> 05:06.080
I'm in class.

05:06.400 --> 05:07.960
How's your interview prep going?

05:07.960 --> 05:09.840
You're replying to messages in class?

05:09.840 --> 05:11.440
Pay attention to your class.

05:11.480 --> 05:12.810
Mind your own business.

05:15.720 --> 05:16.720
Class dismissed.

05:17.400 --> 05:18.040
Xiaocen.

05:18.520 --> 05:19.980
Have you thought about it?

05:20.480 --> 05:21.800
Thought about what?

05:22.960 --> 05:25.420
About helping out at Fang Xiaqing's studio.

05:28.840 --> 05:29.900
Is it appropriate?

05:29.920 --> 05:31.440
Yes, of course it is.

05:32.280 --> 05:34.340
And we can finish our homework there.

05:44.400 --> 05:46.730
Then let's have dinner with them tonight.

05:47.360 --> 05:48.400
Dinner?

05:48.960 --> 05:50.360
You are doing this again.

05:50.560 --> 05:51.840
I just feel

05:52.600 --> 05:53.880
that they might

05:55.280 --> 05:56.960
only want you to go.

05:57.080 --> 05:58.680
I wouldn't be able to help much if I go.

05:58.680 --> 05:59.760
Of course not.

06:03.640 --> 06:05.080
But I...

06:16.640 --> 06:17.280
Xu Xiao.

06:17.840 --> 06:19.440
I think you're very talented.

06:19.440 --> 06:20.500
When you graduate,

06:20.520 --> 06:21.880
you won't even need to look for a job.

06:21.880 --> 06:23.480
Just join Banlan Studio.

06:23.760 --> 06:25.480
We cover food, housing, and getting rich.

06:25.480 --> 06:26.210
How about it?

06:28.880 --> 06:30.010
Actually, my skills

06:30.480 --> 06:32.080
are still a work in progress.

06:32.960 --> 06:33.960
I can give it a try.

06:36.320 --> 06:36.850
Xiaocen,

06:37.720 --> 06:38.720
what do you think?

06:39.680 --> 06:41.159
I... I...

06:41.480 --> 06:42.010
Exactly.

06:43.480 --> 06:44.040
Xiaocen,

06:44.680 --> 06:46.080
we are also looking forward

06:46.080 --> 06:47.480
to your joining.

06:48.840 --> 06:49.800
But

06:50.280 --> 06:52.480
I'm not as capable as Xu Xiao at all.

06:52.800 --> 06:54.659
I'm afraid I won't be of much help.

06:54.920 --> 06:55.580
Who says so?

06:57.640 --> 06:59.570
Your drawing skills are very good.

06:59.760 --> 07:00.800
That's right, Xiaocen.

07:00.800 --> 07:01.760
Don't be modest.

07:02.240 --> 07:03.600
Stay and join us.

07:03.880 --> 07:05.800
Let's create better works together,

07:05.800 --> 07:06.200
okay?

07:06.760 --> 07:07.840
Yeah, please stay.

07:13.040 --> 07:13.680
Okay.

07:13.920 --> 07:15.520
Looking at her, I think she agrees.

07:15.520 --> 07:16.640
Come on, let's have a drink.

07:16.640 --> 07:17.280
Cheers.

07:17.520 --> 07:18.040
Let's drink.

07:18.040 --> 07:18.500
Come on.

07:19.080 --> 07:19.760
Come.

07:19.760 --> 07:21.000
Cheers.

07:26.320 --> 07:27.450
No need to see us off.

07:27.600 --> 07:28.560
From today on,

07:28.640 --> 07:30.160
you are employees of Banlan.

07:30.160 --> 07:31.960
You'll start working tomorrow.

07:32.000 --> 07:33.840
Just come over when you don't have classes.

07:33.840 --> 07:34.320
Okay.

07:34.720 --> 07:35.680
Tell me what you want to eat.

07:35.680 --> 07:36.880
I will make it for you.

07:36.960 --> 07:37.440
Okay.

07:37.440 --> 07:38.840
All right, stop talking,

07:38.840 --> 07:39.760
or it'll be tomorrow.

07:39.760 --> 07:40.360
Bye.

07:40.480 --> 07:41.610
Then we're leaving.

07:41.720 --> 07:41.960
Bye.

07:41.960 --> 07:42.640
Be careful on the road.

07:42.640 --> 07:43.040
Bye.

07:43.400 --> 07:43.880
Bye.

07:47.000 --> 07:48.460
Everyone is so welcoming.

07:49.480 --> 07:49.960
Yeah.

07:53.880 --> 07:55.320
Actually...

07:56.280 --> 07:57.080
What's wrong?

07:58.200 --> 07:59.659
Actually, I was thinking,

08:00.120 --> 08:02.280
since Xia Qing wants your skills,

08:03.840 --> 08:05.440
maybe I won't be of much help.

08:05.520 --> 08:06.450
That's not true.

08:07.280 --> 08:08.880
I'm used to working with you.

08:09.920 --> 08:12.180
From Mr. Yue's class to the antique shop,

08:12.400 --> 08:13.920
I've always worked with you,

08:13.920 --> 08:14.520
haven't I?

08:16.440 --> 08:17.170
Don't worry.

08:17.480 --> 08:18.340
You can do this.

08:19.360 --> 08:19.890
Let's go.

08:21.600 --> 08:22.120
Okay.

08:55.560 --> 08:56.360
Where is this?

08:57.080 --> 08:58.360
It's my friend's pavilion.

08:58.360 --> 09:00.600
It just happens to be vacant these two days.

09:00.600 --> 09:02.000
Why did you bring me here?

09:02.400 --> 09:04.000
Aren't you having an interview soon?

09:04.000 --> 09:05.080
I figured these two days

09:05.080 --> 09:07.080
must be when you're the most nervous.

09:07.080 --> 09:08.520
So I came up with an idea.

09:08.880 --> 09:09.360
Look.

09:12.240 --> 09:13.040
This is...

09:18.840 --> 09:20.400
This is the route map of the museum.

09:20.400 --> 09:20.920
Yes.

09:21.040 --> 09:22.440
Did I draw it accurately?

09:22.960 --> 09:24.160
Why did you draw this?

09:26.040 --> 09:26.640
Now,

09:27.200 --> 09:29.800
just imagine this is the Imperial Kiln Museum.

09:29.800 --> 09:31.200
It is filled with countless

09:31.200 --> 09:32.680
beautiful treasures.

09:33.480 --> 09:36.040
And I am your first visitor.

09:36.040 --> 09:37.960
Now you need to use the lines under your feet

09:37.960 --> 09:39.160
and your memory

09:39.160 --> 09:41.490
to explain all the collections here to me.

09:42.080 --> 09:42.800
Now.

09:44.720 --> 09:46.440
I've paid for a live guide.

09:48.520 --> 09:49.120
All right.

09:51.280 --> 09:51.810
This way.

09:52.960 --> 09:55.160
Welcome to the Jingdezhen Imperial Kiln Museum.

09:55.160 --> 09:56.560
I am your guide, Qi Yi.

09:57.760 --> 09:59.400
The first thing we see

09:59.400 --> 10:01.800
is the treasure of our museum, Ducktor Sui.

10:03.360 --> 10:04.800
From the Chenghua reign of the Ming Dynasty,

10:04.800 --> 10:06.880
it's a plain tri-color duck-shaped incense burner.

10:06.880 --> 10:08.680
Due to the extreme difficulty of the craftsmanship

10:08.680 --> 10:10.760
and the strict selection system of the imperial kiln,

10:10.760 --> 10:13.440
it was broken and buried in Zhushan for over 500 years.

10:13.440 --> 10:16.040
It was unearthed through archaeology in 1987.

10:16.040 --> 10:17.640
It is unique to the imperial kiln,

10:17.640 --> 10:19.480
and no handed-down pieces have been found.

10:19.480 --> 10:21.000
What we are looking at now

10:21.120 --> 10:23.480
is a vat with a blue-and-white cloud dragon design.

10:23.480 --> 10:25.640
Its main purpose is to store water.

10:26.760 --> 10:27.960
What we see next

10:28.200 --> 10:30.600
is the Three-Interconnected-Pot Vessel.

10:32.440 --> 10:32.970
Alright.

10:33.280 --> 10:34.960
That concludes today's explanation.

10:34.960 --> 10:36.160
I hope you enjoyed it.

10:39.200 --> 10:39.920
Look at you.

10:39.920 --> 10:41.960
You don't even need to be in a real museum

10:41.960 --> 10:45.240
to know every piece in the collection like the back of your hand.

10:45.240 --> 10:46.800
You gave such a great blind presentation.

10:46.800 --> 10:47.930
One hundred points.

10:48.000 --> 10:49.040
I wish I could be as relaxed

10:49.040 --> 10:51.370
during the real interview as I am with you.

10:51.400 --> 10:52.720
The reason you get nervous

10:52.720 --> 10:54.040
is because whenever you mention the words

10:54.040 --> 10:55.800
Jingdezhen Imperial Kiln Museum,

10:55.800 --> 10:57.600
it triggers those bad memories.

10:58.040 --> 10:59.370
So I came up with an idea.

10:59.920 --> 11:01.850
I want to create a new memory for you

11:02.120 --> 11:04.160
to erase those bad ones.

11:05.040 --> 11:06.280
A new memory?

11:07.560 --> 11:08.240
Yeah.

11:08.600 --> 11:10.480
I hope you remember today.

11:11.160 --> 11:13.280
In this imaginary museum,

11:13.600 --> 11:14.760
you fluidly

11:14.880 --> 11:17.680
and smoothly explained all the collections to me.

11:18.200 --> 11:20.040
This way, during your interview,

11:20.040 --> 11:21.100
if you get nervous,

11:21.760 --> 11:23.040
you can think of today,

11:23.480 --> 11:24.720
this very moment,

11:25.360 --> 11:26.220
and think of me.

11:28.760 --> 11:29.680
So,

11:30.120 --> 11:31.280
has today's memory

11:31.640 --> 11:33.400
overshadowed the past?

11:36.200 --> 11:36.800
Thank you.

11:44.080 --> 11:45.120
Its name is Xiaoguai.

11:45.120 --> 11:46.840
It used to be a stray cat nearby.

11:46.840 --> 11:49.160
But everyone in our studio often fed it,

11:49.640 --> 11:51.040
so it came by frequently.

11:51.080 --> 11:53.360
Then we gave it baths, trimmed its nails,

11:53.760 --> 11:55.200
and gave it delicious food.

11:55.200 --> 11:56.680
Now it just stays here and won't leave.

11:56.680 --> 11:58.280
It really likes being petted on the head like this.

11:58.280 --> 11:59.160
Xiaoguai.

12:00.280 --> 12:01.160
Xiaoguai.

12:02.600 --> 12:03.530
You are all here.

12:03.680 --> 12:04.210
Let's go.

12:04.480 --> 12:06.200
Come here. I have something to announce.

12:06.200 --> 12:06.730
Let's go.

12:07.360 --> 12:08.840
Let me tell you two something.

12:08.840 --> 12:10.720
Before you two came to Banlan,

12:10.720 --> 12:13.840
Xiaqing and I have been preparing for her solo exhibition.

12:13.840 --> 12:15.400
Holding this exhibition at the same time,

12:15.400 --> 12:16.720
is hoping that more people

12:16.720 --> 12:18.050
can see Xiaqing's works

12:18.560 --> 12:20.840
and our brand, Banlan.

12:21.120 --> 12:22.360
The most important thing is

12:22.360 --> 12:23.400
there is a Mr. Qin.

12:23.920 --> 12:26.440
If he sees the potential of Banlan

12:26.440 --> 12:27.640
and invests heavily,

12:27.800 --> 12:29.800
it will help our brand grow.

12:30.880 --> 12:31.440
Um,

12:31.680 --> 12:32.560
who is Mr. Qin?

12:33.240 --> 12:35.120
He's an investor Jing is negotiating with.

12:35.120 --> 12:36.200
He is someone our studio

12:36.200 --> 12:38.000
is trying to win over right now.

12:39.240 --> 12:41.360
Originally, this exhibition was supposed to

12:41.360 --> 12:42.960
start next week.

12:43.200 --> 12:45.080
But Xiaqing told me

12:45.400 --> 12:47.080
she needs more time

12:47.360 --> 12:49.000
so you guys can help her

12:49.000 --> 12:50.960
polish the final product.

12:51.680 --> 12:53.560
So the exhibition might be postponed.

12:53.560 --> 12:54.240
Got it.

12:55.040 --> 12:56.920
Then knock the two ends of the ceramic staple

12:56.920 --> 12:58.280
we made earlier into the holes.

12:58.280 --> 13:00.810
This way, the broken pieces can be connected.

13:01.680 --> 13:02.400
Let me try.

13:02.920 --> 13:03.400
Sure.

13:04.120 --> 13:05.650
You can start with this one.

13:06.360 --> 13:06.720
Here.

13:08.480 --> 13:08.940
Come on.

13:11.680 --> 13:12.040
Be careful.

13:12.040 --> 13:12.480
Be careful.

13:12.480 --> 13:12.880
Okay.

13:16.880 --> 13:18.360
The finished product looks roughly like this.

13:18.360 --> 13:20.220
Try to cut it as small as possible.

13:20.360 --> 13:21.820
We will still need to knock

13:21.880 --> 13:23.010
and polish it later.

13:27.640 --> 13:28.560
You edit very well.

13:28.560 --> 13:30.290
I found that I learn quite fast.

13:30.360 --> 13:31.160
You are smart.

13:31.480 --> 13:32.880
You learn things easily.

13:38.760 --> 13:40.160
Little Cutie is barking.

13:41.200 --> 13:42.920
Did Jing forget to feed it?

13:43.800 --> 13:44.480
I'll go.

13:45.440 --> 13:46.570
Thank you, Xiaocen.

13:46.600 --> 13:47.400
It's nothing.

13:52.600 --> 13:53.600
Little Cutie,

13:56.040 --> 13:57.370
what are you barking at?

14:02.200 --> 14:02.880
What's wrong?

14:02.880 --> 14:03.440
Xu Xiao,

14:03.920 --> 14:05.120
do you like Xiaocen?

14:06.400 --> 14:07.440
Wh-what?

14:13.520 --> 14:14.520
You are blushing.

14:15.000 --> 14:15.660
No, I am not.

14:16.560 --> 14:17.520
Yes, you are.

14:20.320 --> 14:20.880
No.

14:21.880 --> 14:23.740
We are just ordinary classmates.

14:23.880 --> 14:26.080
You are not just ordinary classmates.

14:26.520 --> 14:28.360
You clearly care about her.

14:29.520 --> 14:30.080
Care?

14:31.120 --> 14:32.480
No, I don't.

14:33.480 --> 14:35.280
Xiaocen just got up and left.

14:35.440 --> 14:37.240
And you started looking for her.

14:37.760 --> 14:39.420
If that's not caring, what is?

14:40.120 --> 14:41.320
Don't talk nonsense.

14:41.960 --> 14:44.290
And don't say anything stupid to Xiaocen.

14:46.840 --> 14:48.570
Little Cutie is indeed hungry.

14:48.720 --> 14:49.080
Sit.

14:55.360 --> 14:56.290
Let's continue.

14:58.960 --> 15:00.560
Why does she want to kill him?

15:01.240 --> 15:03.560
Weren't they enemies in their past lives?

15:03.560 --> 15:04.520
So in this life,

15:04.520 --> 15:06.720
she seeks revenge on him.

15:07.360 --> 15:08.800
Then why didn't he dodge?

15:10.800 --> 15:13.400
He doesn't have the memories of his past life.

15:13.400 --> 15:15.240
He loves her in this life.

15:15.680 --> 15:17.480
When did he fall in love with her?

15:17.560 --> 15:18.320
Sister,

15:18.760 --> 15:19.920
can you just watch the show properly?

15:19.920 --> 15:21.680
You are doing chores while watching it.

15:21.680 --> 15:23.280
You can't follow the plot.

15:24.120 --> 15:26.000
I wouldn't be able to follow it if I didn't ask you.

15:26.000 --> 15:26.640
Just tell me.

15:26.640 --> 15:28.370
Then don't ask me. Ask Xiaocen.

15:28.520 --> 15:30.000
It's distracting me from the show.

15:30.000 --> 15:31.800
Xiaocen, explain it to your mom.

15:33.400 --> 15:34.000
Xiaocen.

15:34.800 --> 15:35.600
What's wrong?

15:36.120 --> 15:37.320
You don't look well.

15:37.520 --> 15:38.780
Did something happen?

15:39.920 --> 15:41.480
What's wrong? Are you not feeling well?

15:41.480 --> 15:42.280
It's nothing.

15:42.680 --> 15:43.610
Really nothing?

15:46.720 --> 15:48.600
What's going on at your school lately?

15:48.600 --> 15:50.680
You used to come straight home after school,

15:50.680 --> 15:52.680
but now you leave early and come back late every day.

15:52.680 --> 15:54.080
She said she went to Taoxichuan.

15:54.080 --> 15:55.940
What did you go to Taoxichuan for?

15:56.840 --> 15:58.480
There's an

15:58.720 --> 15:59.840
older girl outside of school.

15:59.840 --> 16:01.900
She asked me to help her make pottery.

16:02.360 --> 16:02.840
No.

16:03.160 --> 16:05.240
Your schoolwork is already heavy enough.

16:05.240 --> 16:06.160
Things outside of school,

16:06.160 --> 16:07.440
don't get involved in them.

16:07.440 --> 16:08.040
Okay?

16:08.760 --> 16:10.280
You don't need to earn your tuition.

16:10.280 --> 16:11.920
I'm not doing it for money.

16:12.840 --> 16:14.570
If not for money, then what for?

16:16.320 --> 16:17.680
I don't know why either.

16:18.160 --> 16:20.400
You don't know why but you're still doing it?

16:20.400 --> 16:22.460
Are you doing this just to piss me off?

16:22.480 --> 16:24.240
No, Mom.

16:25.280 --> 16:26.880
Sister, keep your voice down.

16:26.880 --> 16:28.680
Look, you frightened the child.

16:28.800 --> 16:30.600
We need to keep Xiaocen happy.

16:30.800 --> 16:32.480
A broad mind leads to a broad body.

16:32.480 --> 16:34.010
First, we need a broad mind.

16:34.640 --> 16:35.360
Yes, yes.

16:35.720 --> 16:36.080
Okay.

16:36.240 --> 16:37.880
I was speaking too loudly.

16:39.000 --> 16:40.880
Let me tell you, things outside of school,

16:40.880 --> 16:42.240
don't get involved in them.

16:42.240 --> 16:43.040
Look at this period of time,

16:43.040 --> 16:44.640
we've finally got your body conditioned.

16:44.640 --> 16:46.360
The doctor also said you can stop taking Chinese medicine.

16:46.360 --> 16:48.720
Don't ruin your health again.

16:48.840 --> 16:49.240
You know?

16:49.240 --> 16:49.880
I know.

16:50.080 --> 16:50.840
Okay, it's late.

16:50.840 --> 16:51.560
Go to sleep.

16:51.920 --> 16:52.560
Go ahead.

16:53.280 --> 16:54.280
Go to sleep early.

17:13.000 --> 17:14.760
With Xu Xiao's help,

17:15.240 --> 17:17.079
Xia Qing made rapid progress.

17:17.640 --> 17:19.900
She quickly found a new approach to work.

17:20.880 --> 17:22.339
The two of them cooperated

17:22.760 --> 17:24.619
with great tacit understanding.

17:25.280 --> 17:27.319
I even felt that in just a few days,

17:27.760 --> 17:28.840
she had gotten closer to Xu Xiao

17:28.840 --> 17:30.480
than I ever was.

17:31.920 --> 17:33.120
I'm always like this.

17:33.200 --> 17:36.720
I'm always several steps slower than others in everything I do.

17:36.720 --> 17:38.240
The way this world works

17:38.600 --> 17:41.260
is like the TV series Aunt and Mom are following.

17:41.840 --> 17:43.840
The fast pace leaves me breathless.

17:46.160 --> 17:48.280
I really hope that my time with Xu Xiao

17:48.960 --> 17:51.440
could be like the bus that took us home,

17:52.000 --> 17:54.400
moving forward slowly, stop by stop.

17:55.840 --> 17:58.570
But I feel like I'm still at the bus stop right now,

17:59.280 --> 18:01.680
not knowing if the last bus hasn't arrived

18:02.400 --> 18:04.000
or has already left.

19:13.440 --> 19:14.040
Xiaocen.

19:15.520 --> 19:16.850
What are you doing here?

19:18.200 --> 19:20.800
I finished the hand-drawn sketches Xiaoyu and Tian Yuan gave me.

19:20.800 --> 19:21.600
Xia Qing,

19:21.600 --> 19:23.040
I'm free right now.

19:23.520 --> 19:24.650
Do you need any help?

19:24.680 --> 19:25.320
No, thanks.

19:25.320 --> 19:26.850
Things are going smoothly.

19:27.600 --> 19:28.640
I made this cake.

19:29.560 --> 19:31.620
Jing and Xu Xiao said it's delicious.

19:31.920 --> 19:33.120
I hope you like it too.

19:34.040 --> 19:34.840
Thank you.

19:35.720 --> 19:37.160
Enjoy. I'll get going.

20:30.440 --> 20:32.000
This is so delicious.

20:54.760 --> 20:55.320
Xiaocen,

20:57.840 --> 20:59.040
did you notice

20:59.480 --> 21:00.960
anything different about Wang Lin and Li Zhuoting

21:00.960 --> 21:02.080
today?

21:03.400 --> 21:04.400
Sorry, Wu Jing.

21:04.400 --> 21:05.640
I didn't hear a word.

21:06.520 --> 21:07.680
Wang Lin, Wang Lin.

21:10.840 --> 21:11.920
They're not sitting together.

21:11.920 --> 21:12.920
Keep it down.

21:13.160 --> 21:13.720
Right.

21:14.120 --> 21:14.980
Let me tell you,

21:15.280 --> 21:16.440
you have no idea.

21:16.920 --> 21:17.800
Xiaoyi...

21:18.240 --> 21:20.160
Things between the three of them are so complicated right now.

21:20.160 --> 21:20.840
Why?

21:21.120 --> 21:24.440
Weren't Xiaoyi and Wang Lin together before?

21:25.000 --> 21:26.280
After they broke up,

21:26.280 --> 21:28.560
Xiaoyi has been flirting with Li Zhuoting.

21:28.560 --> 21:31.080
So now Wang Lin and Li Zhuoting

21:31.080 --> 21:32.880
aren't sitting together anymore.

21:32.880 --> 21:34.010
Look at how far apart

21:34.080 --> 21:35.600
they are sitting.

21:35.600 --> 21:37.600
They're even sitting in a triangle.

21:39.400 --> 21:40.160
Yeah.

21:40.760 --> 21:42.160
It really is a triangle.

21:46.320 --> 21:47.980
Look how awkward they are now.

21:51.520 --> 21:51.850
Look.

21:56.800 --> 21:58.000
Monitor, is everyone here?

21:58.000 --> 21:58.840
Everyone is here.

21:58.840 --> 21:59.440
Then,

21:59.720 --> 22:00.780
let's start class.

22:07.640 --> 22:08.170
Xiaocen.

22:09.440 --> 22:11.360
Are you going to the antique shop today?

22:11.360 --> 22:13.560
Xia Qing and the others went picking porcelain shards this afternoon.

22:13.560 --> 22:15.890
You don't need to go to the studio so early.

22:16.840 --> 22:18.440
I won't go this afternoon.

22:19.760 --> 22:21.620
Yuexin is treating me to milk tea.

22:22.520 --> 22:22.960
Let's go.

22:22.960 --> 22:23.600
Milk tea.

22:30.600 --> 22:31.360
Xiao Xu.

22:32.720 --> 22:34.650
I have something to share with you.

22:35.920 --> 22:38.640
Do you remember my pair of large chicken-heart walnuts?

22:38.640 --> 22:39.440
What's wrong?

22:39.520 --> 22:40.580
A few mornings ago,

22:41.640 --> 22:43.370
as soon as I arrived at the shop,

22:43.600 --> 22:45.680
I realized one was suddenly missing.

22:46.200 --> 22:47.320
I was so anxious that I searched our shop,

22:47.320 --> 22:48.780
upstairs and downstairs.

22:49.360 --> 22:50.200
It has been with me for over ten years.

22:50.200 --> 22:51.760
I'm attached to it, you know?

22:51.760 --> 22:52.680
Most importantly,

22:52.680 --> 22:53.200
it's called a large chicken heart.

22:53.200 --> 22:55.320
If I lose one, wouldn't that mean I'm missing a heart?

22:55.320 --> 22:57.050
That's not the strangest part.

22:57.280 --> 22:58.540
The strangest thing is

22:58.800 --> 23:00.060
that in the afternoon,

23:00.480 --> 23:02.320
it suddenly appeared on my desk,

23:02.320 --> 23:03.400
in the most conspicuous place.

23:03.400 --> 23:04.060
Right here.

23:04.320 --> 23:05.450
Right in the middle.

23:06.320 --> 23:08.320
Don't you think this is too strange?

23:10.680 --> 23:11.640
How come when I share something with you,

23:11.640 --> 23:13.000
I get no feedback at all?

23:16.240 --> 23:18.370
Didn't I tell you to come with Xiaocen?

23:19.480 --> 23:21.720
There's a bunch of cups in the shop waiting for her to write on.

23:21.720 --> 23:22.920
You can't just grab her

23:22.920 --> 23:24.040
as soon as she has a break.

23:24.040 --> 23:25.240
She needs to rest too.

23:26.720 --> 23:27.850
From the sound of it,

23:28.240 --> 23:29.770
there seems to be a problem.

23:32.160 --> 23:32.960
What's wrong?

23:33.440 --> 23:33.970
Nothing.

23:35.280 --> 23:36.200
Did you two have a fight?

23:36.200 --> 23:36.760
No.

23:36.960 --> 23:38.020
Then what's wrong?

23:41.360 --> 23:41.920
Well,

23:43.840 --> 23:45.080
I feel like she's

23:45.600 --> 23:48.060
suddenly become a different person lately.

23:48.960 --> 23:50.320
Did you make her mad?

23:50.800 --> 23:52.560
Mad? Mad about what?

23:53.160 --> 23:54.560
Mad about what?

23:57.120 --> 23:59.180
How would I know what she's mad about?

23:59.720 --> 24:01.720
Let me tell you, stop overthinking.

24:01.960 --> 24:03.200
When it comes to women,

24:03.200 --> 24:05.330
even if you pay 120 percent attention,

24:05.640 --> 24:07.640
you still can't avoid stepping on landmines.

24:07.640 --> 24:08.720
When I, your boss, was young,

24:08.720 --> 24:10.450
I suffered a lot in this regard.

24:10.640 --> 24:11.770
Stop overthinking.

24:11.800 --> 24:12.960
Women.

24:13.840 --> 24:15.570
I didn't get it when I was young.

24:15.960 --> 24:17.000
I don't get it now.

24:17.440 --> 24:18.640
And in the future,

24:18.960 --> 24:20.220
I doubt I will, either.

24:36.080 --> 24:36.800
Xu Xiao.

24:37.040 --> 24:38.170
Reply to him. Hurry.

24:51.280 --> 24:52.240
Xu Xiao.

24:55.320 --> 24:55.850
Xiaocen.

24:57.840 --> 24:59.570
Why did you ask me to come today?

25:02.720 --> 25:03.780
I want to sincerely

25:04.480 --> 25:05.480
apologize to you.

25:06.720 --> 25:07.400
Apologize?

25:11.040 --> 25:11.770
Have you been

25:12.720 --> 25:13.720
unhappy lately?

25:16.600 --> 25:17.360
No.

25:19.840 --> 25:21.770
I know you've been unhappy lately.

25:22.280 --> 25:23.080
I also know

25:23.520 --> 25:26.120
that you're not someone who gets angry easily.

25:27.760 --> 25:28.800
I can be a bit slow

25:29.160 --> 25:30.620
when dealing with people.

25:31.400 --> 25:33.260
Sometimes I make people unhappy.

25:33.520 --> 25:34.200
So,

25:35.280 --> 25:36.280
is it my fault

25:37.680 --> 25:38.720
that you're unhappy?

25:38.720 --> 25:39.850
It's not your fault.

25:41.440 --> 25:42.480
It's me.

25:45.040 --> 25:45.800
Young man,

25:45.800 --> 25:47.730
buy a balloon for your girlfriend.

25:47.760 --> 25:48.400
Sorry.

25:51.440 --> 25:53.640
We are not in that kind of relationship.

25:53.800 --> 25:55.130
It doesn't seem like it.

25:58.040 --> 26:00.570
Then what can I do to make you a little happier?

26:02.640 --> 26:03.240
Young man.

26:03.320 --> 26:05.320
Buy a balloon for your girlfriend and she will be happy.

26:05.320 --> 26:06.450
You can cheer her up.

26:06.600 --> 26:07.080
Get one.

26:08.480 --> 26:08.960
Get one.

26:09.480 --> 26:10.280
Do you want it?

26:12.120 --> 26:12.780
No, thanks.

26:14.800 --> 26:16.930
You really don't need it? I'm leaving.

26:22.640 --> 26:23.080
Sir.

26:23.760 --> 26:24.400
Xu Xiao.

26:25.120 --> 26:25.760
How much is it?

26:25.760 --> 26:26.280
Five.

26:27.000 --> 26:27.800
I'll scan your code.

26:27.800 --> 26:28.160
Okay.

26:28.240 --> 26:28.840
Thank you.

26:35.160 --> 26:35.800
Do you

26:36.480 --> 26:37.160
want this?

26:44.600 --> 26:45.040
Is this

26:45.400 --> 26:47.560
for me?

26:50.120 --> 26:51.360
If it makes you happy,

26:53.240 --> 26:53.900
here you go.

27:09.280 --> 27:09.960
Thank you.

27:12.000 --> 27:12.600
Young man,

27:12.760 --> 27:14.120
did you cheer up your girlfriend?

27:14.120 --> 27:15.780
If not, how about another one?

27:15.800 --> 27:16.460
No, thanks.

27:16.720 --> 27:17.520
One is enough.

27:17.520 --> 27:18.250
Are you sure?

27:19.120 --> 27:20.040
I'm really leaving then.

27:20.040 --> 27:20.640
Thank you.

27:30.080 --> 27:30.760
Let's go.

27:32.640 --> 27:33.120
Let's go.
